    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Oneiro is an office worker who is forced to stay all night drafting reports to avoid being fired from his job. His boss asks him to draft 8 reports and submit them every hour and a half.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146700/extras/8c361b2b233fd532c982d6f23231eb3a.poster.avif?t=1734520305\" width=504 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146700/extras/8c361b2b233fd532c982d6f23231eb3a.webm?t=1734520305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146700/extras/8c361b2b233fd532c982d6f23231eb3a.mp4?t=1734520305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each time Oneiro finishes a report, he will fall asleep and have a dream that he must overcome to avoid getting stuck in the dream world (and completely asleep at work).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146700/extras/bc933a5e458bdd1b17c25a759d306bb9.poster.avif?t=1734520305\" width=504 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146700/extras/bc933a5e458bdd1b17c25a759d306bb9.webm?t=1734520305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146700/extras/bc933a5e458bdd1b17c25a759d306bb9.mp4?t=1734520305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What you can find:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > It can last 40 minutes or more, depending on your skill.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > It has 4 endings that depend on the number of mistakes you make.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > It has 3 difficulty levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > It has 7 challenges (achievements). </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > It has 7 unique minigames.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Custom music for each minigame.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > It has 3 cinematics.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146700/extras/815372b9923d8812e281b0d08a33f7cf.poster.avif?t=1734520305\" width=504 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146700/extras/815372b9923d8812e281b0d08a33f7cf.webm?t=1734520305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146700/extras/815372b9923d8812e281b0d08a33f7cf.mp4?t=1734520305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
